{"tid":1698651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集講流亡台灣手足，入黎比啲支持佢地","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:47:34.000Z","uid":305017,"like":216,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"e5475568afc78d8247c2e590e4d398fba308638c","tid":1698651,"uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"link: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/JAkrBdjGVmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJAkrBdjGVmE&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a9018d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JAkrBdjGVmE</a><br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集訪問左幾個流亡台灣既手足<br />\n有手足覺得好灰，去到台灣只能夠睇住香港既情況，乜都做唔到，而自己好似懦夫咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我想講，你地絕對唔係懦夫!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝你地之前既付出，你地唔係condom，香港手足冇忘記你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">好好照顧自己，期待煲底重聚一刻!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比啲支持流亡既手足</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835bb8d5c21fd060d07a20ff7f424a1a395cef53","tid":1698651,"uid":726,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"rthk youtube本身有但無端端落左架，唔知咩事"},{"pid":"6de6437b9e6426400b11b8b31c0c02b2630662bf","tid":1698651,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c38e78df02aaa3621e228bb5a7322ab8d4e66f0","tid":1698651,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"reply