-11-07T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"我怕你老母捱唔過聽朝添啊"},{"pid":"ecfc711962235e355857771e790943bec116d126","tid":1698651,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba84969b0dd6858348d84a290a5d37d5c7a6fe2","tid":1698651,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68366f66d69572f65ecdbb6eb19c36e58925a00d","tid":1698651,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:57:11.000Z","msg":"手足煲底見"},{"pid":"1e95927c5ee9988f5cd2363e407c543342724593","tid":1698651,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:57:16.000Z","msg":"可以台灣擺街站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceabe3438dcf31da1a3f333bc725dfd980e90da","tid":1698651,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dL169vQq5DU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdL169vQq5DU&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=5a1d309e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dL169vQq5DU</a><br />\n大家都幫幫手<br />\n兩位主持盡心盡力又出錢幫手足 仲想請埋手足打工<br />\n其中一位仲係律師 有親身接觸前線巴絲"},{"pid":"b29936539b0ffc66231f0197e18e5b451e60ea5e","tid":1698651,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"手足你哋還好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2b15eade195288265aa4a528879864fb3731f","tid":1698651,"uid":254881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5475568afc78d8247c2e590e4d398fba308638c","tid":1698651,"uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"link: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/JAkrBdjGVmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJAkrBdjGVmE&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a9018d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JAkrBdjGVmE</a><br />\n<br />\n鏗鏘集訪問左幾個流亡台灣既手足<br />\n有手足覺得好灰，去到台灣只能夠睇住香港既情況，乜都做唔到，而自己好似懦夫咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我想講，你地絕對唔係懦夫!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝你地之前既付出，你地唔係condom，香港手足冇忘記你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">好好照顧自己，期待煲底重聚一刻!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比啲支持流亡既手足</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75f64fc636d7fe05c8c59af479f1ab9d46e93b50","tid":1698651,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"大家無怪責你地 錯係政權和它的打手黑警 幕後的中共 迫你地要走<br />\n反而多謝你地既付出 而家只係轉崗位做幕後 台灣戰線的重任由你地幫手開拓"},{"pid":"f0554913dc12ecaa5608c2563285d704c347416a","tid":1698651,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"❤️"},{"pid":"072f800ecd8d0e189594e626cc1330e6a451352e","tid":1698651,"uid":39842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97eb8528fdf045dab8243c93f601b3737acb4be4","tid":1698651,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61bcd7822980adb672c283620b790a90c850dee9","tid":1698651,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"曾經同幾班想幫台灣手足嘅連登仔接觸，但都come唔到一個好嘅幫助方案，主要都係互信可靠嘅渠道問題，始終冇大台，同埋係要暗地做，邊個唔係有名譽地位嘅行出嚟話牽頭，兩邊都會有人唔信，最後都係講講吓收皮。"},{"pid":"6a0baef054a6247926c0397e4d10a7d958bc12ff","tid":1698651,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:12:32.000Z","msg":"希望真係大家come到一個好嘅辦法出嚟幫佢哋"},{"pid":"ba49661117e6293c349c0d5e5d9c0b99fd09f2a5","tid":1698651,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21da28fd236b7d95f106a5d54ff56da808a9bad7","tid":1698651,"uid":279313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人會怪你地係懦夫架!<br />\n加油!希望有日我地係煲底相見!"},{"pid":"9d5806f05b1d5c5134bda50e79798b51f821713a","tid":1698651,"uid":272165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:45:57.000Z","msg":"我哋一定會係煲底再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93982abc07aa961dc4ecd351935a9a34d53f64b","tid":1698651,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67270a15708f4780b85205b17cce65e165a56b3a","tid":1698651,"uid":15933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"7月1係呢場運動好大嘅轉捩點，佢地付出絕對不能被抹殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm